Let's build another script, which will download the daily report at:
https://buttondown.com/agent-k/archive/llm-daily-{month}-{day}-2025/
month could be july for example, day could be 06 for example
You need to use 
https://r.jina.ai/buttondown.com/agent-k/archive/llm-daily-{month}-{day}-2025/ to convert the website to markdown and save if to local folder.
The script should accept month and day as arguments, then you pull the full week of daily reports. for example, if month is july and day is 06, you should pull the daily reports from 06 to 12. if the report is not available, you should skip it and print a warning message. And the folder name should be {month}-{day}







